text: Player experience Texas Christian University: 2023/2024 Texas University:2020/2021 - 2022/2023 Tigres UANL:2017/2018 - 2018/2019 Melanie Guadalupe Parra Quintero (born 12 September 2002) is a Mexican volleyball player. She played at the 2019 FIVB U20 Women's World Championship and 2018 FIVB Women's World Championship. She played for Sinaloa. Melanie Parra has garnered Big 12 Offensive Player of the Week honors. == References == ==Other websites== * MELANIE GUADALUPE PARRA QUINTERO, volleymob * Melanie Parra, women.volleybox.net/ * Melanie Parra Quintero - Player Info, globalsportsarchive.com/ Category:2002 births Category:Living people Category:Mexican volleyball players
